detail_desc: Jumper in a soft, chunky knit with dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.

Blouse in a patterned viscose weave with a small, frilled collar, a V-neck opening with narrow ties at the top and covered buttons down the front. Long raglan sleeves with elastication and a lace-trimmed frill at the cuffs, an elasticated seam at the hem and a gently flared, lace-trimmed peplum. Unlined.
Long-sleeved jersey top with lace at the back. Open section at the back with a button at the back of the neck.

Trousers in a cotton weave with a lightly brushed finish. Regular waist, a concealed hook-and-eye fastening, zip fly, side pockets and welt back pockets with a button. Adjustable tab with buttons at the sides and gently tapered, ankle-length legs.
Straight-cut top in woven fabric with a slight sheen, V-neck and spaghetti straps.
Earrings with plastic beads and tassels. Length 8.5 cm.
Top in soft cotton jersey with reversible sequins, short sleeves with sewn-in turn-ups and a gently rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.

Tunic woven in an airy viscose blend with hole embroidery and inset lace sections. Frill-trimmed stand-up collar, a button placket and pin-tucks at the front. 3/4-length sleeves with pin-tucks and narrow cuffs, and a seam at the waist with tiers to the hem. Slightly longer underdress.
Fine-knit moccasins with soft terry inside, imitation leather trims and soft suede soles.
Scarf in patterned satin that can also be tied as a hairband. Size 55x55 cm. The polyester content of the scarf is partly recycled.

All-in-one suit in soft sweatshirt fabric made from an organic cotton blend. Small, ribbed stand-up collar, long raglan sleeves, a zip down the front that continues down one leg and foldover ribbing at the cuffs and hems. Soft brushed inside.
Satin top in a relaxed fit with a lace section at the top and narrow, adjustable shoulder straps.
Gently tailored jacket in woven fabric with notch lapels, a button at the front, welt front pockets with a flap, and a single back vent. Lined.

Padded parka in woven fabric with a faux fur-lined hood with a detachable, foldover faux fur trim. Zip with a wind flap and concealed press-studs down the front, a drawstring at the waist, side pockets with press-studs and a zipped sleeve pocket. Inner ribbing at the cuffs and a single back vent with a drawstring. Quilted lining.
Flounced skirt in a stretch weave. Wrapover front with ties at one side and a concealed zip at the back. Unlined.
Knee-length skirt in an airy patterned weave with fringing. Concealed zip and a slit at the back. Lined.
Soft pile fancy dress hat in the shape of a cat’s head with padding, embroidery and sewn-on ears. Hook and loop fastener at the front. Lined. Polyester padding.
Set with a hat and tube scarf in soft cotton jersey.
Short suede skirt with a visible zip at the back and seam at the hem. Lined.
Mules with pointed toes and a decorative knot detail at the front. Imitation leather insoles and thermoplastic rubber (TPR) soles.
Fully lined, 5-pocket slim-fit jeans in washed, stretch denim with hard-worn details. Adjustable, elasticated waist, zip fly and narrow hems.
T-shirt in printed cotton jersey.
Twill cap with an appliqué on the front and an adjustable plastic fastener at the back.

Padded parka in woven fabric with a lined hood with a detachable faux fur trim. Zip and wind flap with hook-and-loop fastening down the front, flap chest and front pockets with a press-stud and two additional zipped front pockets. Concealed drawstring at the waist and inner ribbing at the cuffs. Lined.
Boys' briefs in cotton jersey with an elasticated waist and lined front.
Sandals in imitation suede with hook and loop fastenings. Imitation suede linings and insoles, and fluted soles.
Elasticated scrunchie in woven fabric.
Bra in microfibre and lace with underwired, moulded, lightly padded cups that shape the bust and provide good support. Narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and a hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Socks in a soft, fine-knit cotton blend with elasticated tops.

Sports trousers in sturdy jersey with an elasticated drawstring waist and side pockets with a concealed zip. Legs with taped details, a small reflective print at one side and ribbed hems. The polyester content of the trousers is recycled.
Top in soft jersey with a glittery print motif on the front, short sleeves and narrow ribbing around the neckline.

Zip-through hoodie in sweatshirt fabric made from an organic cotton and recycled polyester blend with a soft brushed inside. Jersey-lined hood, a zip down the front, front pockets and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Knee-length, 5-pocket skirt in washed, stretch denim with a zip fly and button and slit at the front. The skirt is made partly from recycled cotton.
Cap in cotton twill with an adjustable metal fastening at the back.
Long-sleeved top in soft jersey with gathers at the top and lace sections on the shoulders.
Underwired bra in lace with removable inserts that shape the bust and provide good support. Adjustable shoulder straps, a hook-and-eye fastening at the back, and a wide lace trim at the hem.
V-neck T-shirt in soft, organic cotton jersey.
Top in soft sweatshirt fabric. Slightly looser fit with dropped shoulders and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Metal earrings with faceted plastic stones. Clips at the top for extra stability. Length approx. 4 cm.
Whooli Chen x H&M. Set with a double-layered hat and matching tube scarf in soft, patterned, organic cotton jersey. The hat has a small woven appliqué at the front.
Jumper in a soft, fine knit containing some wool with a gentle V-neck, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. The polyester content of the jumper is recycled.

Short jacket in patterned cotton twill with a collar and concealed buttons down the front. Flap chest pockets with a button, welt side pockets and long sleeves with shaping seams and a button at the cuffs. Unlined.
Imitation suede sandals with a zip at the heel. Fabric linings, imitation leather insoles and rubber soles. Covered heels, 7 cm.
Sports boxer shorts in fast-drying, breathable functional fabric with an elasticated waist.

Outdoor jacket in woven fabric with a double-layered hood, stand up collar and zip down the front with a chin guard. Padded front and back sections, zipped side pockets, long raglan sleeves with thumbholes at the cuffs and inset side panels in sturdy jersey lined with thermal fleece. Longer and rounded at the back. Partly lined.
Fine-knit liner socks designed to be hidden inside your shoes. The socks have a ribbed section in the middle of the foot and elastication around the openings for optimum comfort.
Hair elastic and hair clip in metal covered in plastic beads. Length of hair clip 8 cm.
Cardigan in a soft, fine-knit viscose blend with long dolman sleeves, no buttons and slits in the sides. Slightly longer at the back.
A pair of metal earrings in the shape of skeletons decorated with rhinestones. The zinc content of the earrings is recycled.
Ankle-length, pull-on trousers in an airy weave with a regular, elasticated waist, welt side pockets and fake back pockets. Loose fit with a fake fly and tapered legs with creases.

Platform sandals in braided jute with imitation leather details and block heels. Crossover foot straps and an adjustable ankle strap with a metal buckle. Imitation leather insoles. Platform front approx. 4 cm. Heel approx. 8 cm.
High-waisted jeans in washed superstretch denim with a zip fly and button, fake front pockets, real back pockets and super-skinny legs.
Long-sleeved top in a soft rib knit containing glittery threads with an open neckline with a small stand-up collar attached at the back.

Fully lined cargo trousers in a cotton weave with an adjustable, elasticated waist, zip fly and button, diagonal front pockets, a fake flap back pocket and flap leg pockets with a hook and loop fastening. Tapered legs with shaping seams and ribbed hems. Jersey lining.
Fitted, off-the-shoulder top in soft jersey made from a viscose blend with a V-neck front and back and long sleeves.
Poncho in a soft, fine knit with a draped neckline and open sides. Length at the front and back approx. 70 cm.

Set with a T-shirt and pair of shorts in soft cotton. T-shirt in jersey with a press-stud on one shoulder (except in sizes 1½-4Y) and print motif on the front. Shorts in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with covered elastication and a drawstring at the waist, diagonal side pockets and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems.

Lightly padded, thermal jacket with a stand-up collar and detachable, lined hood with narrow elastication and a concealed hook and loop fastening. Zip down the front with a chin guard, welt side pockets, two inner pockets and reflective details. Lined.
Biker jacket in washed stretch twill with hard worn details and notch lapels with decorative buttons. Diagonal zip at the front, zipped side pockets and a zip at the cuffs. Unlined.
Double-breasted, hooded cardigan in soft, purl-knit cotton with heart-shaped buttons at the top.
Flared trousers in stretch twill with an elasticated waist, fake front pockets and real back pockets.
Glasses with plastic frames and clear lenses.

Shirt in an airy, slub cotton weave with a grandad collar, buttons down the front and yoke with a pleat at the back. Chest pocket, long sleeves with a tab and button, buttoned cuffs, and a gently rounded hem.
Fine-knit trainer socks in a soft cotton blend with elasticated tops.
Sleeveless dress in cotton jersey with a V-neck, double-layered top and flounced,trimmed shoulder straps with broderie anglaise. Elasticated seam at the waist and ties at the back.

KAROLINA KIJAK x H&M. Bomber jacket in patterned satin with a zip down the front, long raglan sleeves and discreet pockets in the side seams. Small, ribbed stand-up collar with a glittery edge, and the same ribbing with a glittery edge at the cuffs and hem. Lined.
Short skirt in woven fabric with large flounces at the front and hem and a concealed zip at the back. Lined.
Short shorts in soft, patterned jersey with an elasticated waist and side pockets.
Calf-length cotton dress in a patterned crêpe weave with wide smocking and frill trims. Detachable, adjustable shoulder straps at the top and a seam at the waist. Unlined.
Sports tights in fast-drying functional fabric with an elasticated waist.
Hipster briefs in microfibre with lace trims, a low waist, lined gusset and cutaway coverage at the back.
Hi-tops in imitation leather with a lightly padded edge and tongue, elasticated lacing at the front and an adjustable hook and loop tab. Soft pile linings and insoles and rubber soles.
Ankle-length trousers in ribbed jersey with a sheen. Elasticated waist and wide, straight-cut legs with raw-edge hems.
T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a draped tie detail at the hem.
Hair clip in recycled metal with artificial pearls and sparkly stones and three pendants. Length 8.5 cm.
Leggings in sturdy jersey with covered elastication at the waist and side stripes.
T-shirt in cotton jersey with a print motif.
Lined triangle bikini top with removable inserts, a frill trim at the hem and ties at the back and back of the neck.
